'''[[伏伊伏丁那|伏伊伏丁那]]省旗'''由紅、藍、白三色條紋組成。其中藍色部分中有三顆黃色五角星，象征組成佛伊弗迪納的三個地區—[[巴奇卡|巴奇卡]]，[[巴納特|巴納特]]和[[斯雷姆|斯雷姆]]。伏伊伏丁那另有一面傳統旗幟，是從上至下的紅藍白三色條紋<ref name=freeeurope>{{cite web | url=http://www.slobodnaevropa.org/a/grb-vojvodine-trobojka/27990027.html | title=Uz grb Vojvodine i trobojka srpska | publisher=Radio Free Europe | date=15 September 2016 | accessdate=30 September 2016 | author=Šinković, Norbert | language=Serbo-Croatian | archive-date=2016-09-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916192637/http://www.slobodnaevropa.org/a/grb-vojvodine-trobojka/27990027.html }}</ref>。

